External Knowledge: 
 The usernames 'john_doe' and 'jane_doe' are specific user identifiers; 
 The 'failure' status refers to the unsuccessful builds; 
 The 'average failure rate' is calculated based on the 'metric_value' in the 'build_metrics' table.

sql:
SELECT artifact_name 
FROM build_artifacts 
WHERE build_id = 0;

SELECT DISTINCT bc.config_name
FROM build_configurations bc
JOIN builds b ON bc.config_id = b.build_config_id;

SELECT target_name 
FROM targets 
WHERE target_id = 0;
